    "last_activity_date" : 1526973273,
    "creation_date" : 1526973273,
    "answer_id" : 50461845,
    "question_id" : 1447407,
    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>For Best solution, Use async/await statement for ecma script 2017</p>\n\n<p><strong>await can use only inside of async function</strong> </p>\n\n<pre><code>function sleep(time) {\n    return new Promise((resolve) =&gt; {\n        setTimeout(resolve, time || 1000);\n    });\n}\n\nawait sleep(10000); //this method wait for 10 sec.\n</code></pre>\n\n<p><strong><em>Note : async / await not actualy stoped thread like Thread.sleep but simulate it</em></strong></p>\n"
  } ],
